description: Ministry of City Planning and Water Supply - Orders made to approve the acquisition of the immovable properties in Karanduwawala, Yahalathenna, Harispattuwa D/S Division, Kandy District for the constructions under the Yahalathenna Water Supply Scheme and in Siyambalawala, Ruwanwella D/S Division, Kegalle District for the construction under Greater Ruwanwella Water Proposal Scheme and in Debarawewa, Tissamaharamaya D/S Division, Hambantota District for the constructions under Tissamaharamaya Water Supply Scheme
